text.section: The definitions in § 1-101 of this article do not apply to the Interstate Compact set forth in § 7-1303 of this subtitle.

In the Interstate Compact set forth in § 7-1303 of this subtitle, unless the context clearly requires otherwise, "article", "section", and "subsection" mean an article, section, and subsection, respectively, of the Interstate Compact.
